00:00:08.820 --> 00:00:10.672 align:middle line:84%
>>People are basically
going to keep on

00:00:10.672 --> 00:00:13.660 align:middle line:84%
to help uncover what
really happened.

00:00:13.660 --> 00:00:15.610 align:middle line:84%
>>I felt like something
