of your gold friends

00:16:48.430 --> 00:16:51.020 align:middle line:84%
that were coming on the show,
and people talking about that.

00:16:51.020 --> 00:16:51.686 align:middle line:90%
We're going to--

00:16:51.686 --> 00:16:52.630 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: $8,000 gold--

00:16:52.630 --> 00:16:54.770 align:middle line:84%
>>CURTIS: $5,000,
$6,000, whatever.

