and be totally refreshing.

00:26:27.420 --> 00:26:31.580 align:middle line:84%
Because I think people may be
tired of these little family

00:26:31.580 --> 00:26:32.080 align:middle line:90%
dynasties.

00:26:32.080 --> 00:26:37.170 align:middle line:84%
>>CURTIS: Well, there
are dark horses all over.

00:26:37.170 --> 00:26:39.430 align:middle line:84%
A lot of people throughout
the history of mankind

00:26:39.430 --> 00:26:42.450 align:middle line:84%
have always wanted some kind of
dark horse to come rescue them.

00:26:42.450 --> 00:26:45.610 align:middle line:90%
We all know what that means.

